# The raw SBML corpus is large (~273 MB) and is NEVER committed.
# It is reconstructed locally by fetch.py / copied from a mirror, then
# crawled in place by filter.py. Only manifest.csv (the reproducible
# good/bad partition) and the scripts are tracked.
data/

